This app is a a AI chatbot that allows the user to chat with AI, call tools and produce documents in a canvas in a right panel.

# Architecture

The server is a single file located at [main.tsx](mdc:src/server/main.tsx) the whole AI logic is there.

The client is in the [src/](mdc:src) folder (exluding the [src/server/](mdc:src/server) folder).

The client uses Tailwind 4, React 19, assistant-ui and blocknote for the canvas feature.
